text.section:
In this section, "equity security" means:
stock or a similar security;
a security convertible, with or without consideration, into stock or a similar security;
a security carrying a warrant or right to subscribe to or purchase stock or a similar security;
any other warrant or right to subscribe to or purchase stock or a similar security; or
any other security that the Commissioner considers to be of a similar nature and necessary or appropriate to treat as an equity security, based on regulations adopted by the Commissioner in the public interest or to protect investors.
